    ⚠️ 4.0.0-beta.0 / 2021-11-16 - Name change of many configuration properties. - attrNodeName to attributesGroupName - attrValueProcessor to attributeValueProcessor - parseNodeValue to parseTagValue - ignoreNameSpace to removeNSPrefix - numParseOptions to numberParseOptions - spelling correction for suppressEmptyNode - Name change of cli and browser bundle to fxparser - isArray option is added to parse a tag into array - preserveOrder option is added to render XML in such a way that the result js Object maintains the order of properties same as in XML. - Processing behaviour of tagValueProcessor and attributeValueProcessor are changes with extra input parameters - j2xparser is renamed to XMLBuilder. - You need to build XML parser instance for given options first before parsing XML. - fix #327, #336: throw error when extra text after XML content - fix #330: attribute value can have '\n', - fix #350: attrbiutes can be separated by '\n' from tagname
